00014 bool CABIDDLMTracer::checkSSS( const STreeNode *node, int depth ) const
00015 {

00039 STreeTrace * CABIDDLMTracer::trace( const STreeNode *rootNode, int depth ) const
00040 {
00041     STreeTrace *newTrace = new STreeTrace;
00042     newTrace->s_aiName = name();
00043     newTrace->s_columnNames = 
00044         QString("call|open|eval|value|a,B|best action,value").split('|');
00045     
00046     if( rootNode == NULL )
00047         return newTrace;
00048     if( rootNode->s_childList.isEmpty() )
00049         return newTrace;
00050     
00051     int d;
00052     STreeCall *curDepth;
00053     for( d = 1; d <= depth; ++d )
00054     {
00055         curDepth = new STreeCall;
00056         traceCall( curDepth, rootNode, d, -INF, INF, true );
00057         
00058         ((SABIDDLMLine*)(*curDepth)[0])->s_call = 
00059                                         QString("DLM(%1,%2,-INF,INF)")
00060                                         .arg(rootNode->s_name)
00061                                         .arg(d);
00062         ((SABIDDLMLine*)(curDepth->s_lines.last()))->s_boxAction = true;
00063         ((SABIDDLMLine*)(curDepth->s_lines.last()))->s_boxValue = false;
00064         
00065         newTrace->s_depths.append( curDepth );
00066     }
00067     
00068     return newTrace;
00069 }

00071 void CABIDDLMTracer::traceCall( STreeCall *call, const STreeNode *node,
00072                      int depth, float alpha, float beta, bool max ) const
00073 {
00074     if( call == NULL || node == NULL )
00075         return;
00076 
00077     QString open;
00078     STreeNode *curNode;
00079     foreach( curNode, node->s_childList )
00080         open += curNode->s_name + " ";
00081     open = open.simplified();
00082     
00083     SABIDDLMLine *curLine;
00084     QString bestAction;
00085     float bestValue = -1;
00086     float curAlpha = alpha, curBeta = beta;
00087     bool better;
00088     foreach( curNode, node->s_childList )
00089     {
00090         curLine = new SABIDDLMLine;
00091         
00092         curLine->s_open = open;
00093         curLine->s_eval = open.section( ' ', 0, 0 );
00094         open = open.section( ' ', 1, -1 );
00095         
00096         curLine->s_valueCall = max?"Min":"Max";
00097         curLine->s_valueCall += QString("V(%1,%2,%3,%4)")
00098                                 .arg(curNode->s_name)
00099                                 .arg(depth-1)
00100                                 .arg(SABIDDLMLine::numberToString(curAlpha))
00101                                 .arg(SABIDDLMLine::numberToString(curBeta));
00102         if( curNode->s_childList.count() == 0 || depth == 1 )
00103         {
00104             curLine->s_valueValue = curNode->s_value;
00105             curLine->s_sss = false;
00106         }
00107         else if( checkSSS( curNode, depth - 1 ) )
00108         {
00109             curLine->s_valueValue = sssValue( curNode, depth - 1 );
00110             curLine->s_sss = true;
00111         }
00112         else
00113         {
00114             call->s_children.append( new STreeCall() );
00115             traceCall( call->s_children.last(), curNode, depth-1,
00116                        curAlpha, curBeta, !max );
00117             curLine->s_valueValue = call->s_children.last()->s_returnValue;
00118         }
00119         
00120         if( bestAction.isEmpty() )
00121             better = true;
00122         else
00123         {
00124             if( max )   better = (curLine->s_valueValue > bestValue );
00125             else        better = (curLine->s_valueValue < bestValue );
00126         }
00127         if( better )
00128         {
00129             bestAction = node->s_name + curNode->s_name;
00130             bestValue = curLine->s_valueValue;
00131             
00132             if( max )
00133             {
00134                 if( bestValue > curBeta )
00135                     curLine->s_prune = true;
00136                 else if( bestValue > curAlpha )
00137                     curAlpha = bestValue;
00138             }
00139             else
00140             {
00141                 if( bestValue < curAlpha )
00142                     curLine->s_prune = true;
00143                 else if( bestValue < curBeta )
00144                     curBeta = bestValue;
00145             }
00146         }
00147         
00148         curLine->s_alpha = curAlpha;
00149         curLine->s_beta = curBeta;
00150         
00151         curLine->s_bestAction = bestAction;
00152         curLine->s_bestValue = bestValue;
00153         
00154         call->s_lines.append( curLine );
00155         
00156         if( curLine->s_prune )
00157             break;
00158         
00159         if( curLine->s_sss )
00160         {
00161             if( curLine->s_valueValue <= curLine->s_alpha )
00162                 curLine->s_prune = true;
00163             else if( curLine->s_valueValue >= curLine->s_beta )
00164                 curLine->s_prune = true;
00165         }
00166     }
00167     
00168     call->s_returnValue = bestValue;
00169     ((SABIDDLMLine*)call->s_lines.first())->s_call = 
00170         QString(max?"MaxV(%1,%2,%3,%4)":"MinV(%1,%2,%3,%4)")
00171         .arg(node->s_name)
00172         .arg(depth)
00173         .arg(SABIDDLMLine::numberToString(alpha))
00174         .arg(SABIDDLMLine::numberToString(beta));
00175     ((SABIDDLMLine*)call->s_lines.last())->s_boxValue = true;
00176 }

00211 QString SABIDDLMLine::operator [](int index)
00212 {
00213     QString ret;
00214     
00215     switch( index )
00216     {
00217     case 0: //  CALL
00218         ret = s_call;
00219         break;        
00220     case 1: //  OPEN
00221         ret = s_open;
00222         break;   
00223     case 2: //  EVAL
00224         ret = s_open.section(' ', 0, 0);
00225         break;   
00226     case 3: //  VALUE
00227         ret = s_valueCall;
00228         ret += "=" + QString::number( s_valueValue );
00229         if( s_sss || s_prune )
00230         {
00231             ret += " (";
00232             if( s_sss )
00233             {
00234                 ret += "SSS";
00235                 if( s_prune )
00236                     ret += ",";
00237             }
00238             if( s_prune )
00239                 ret += "prune";
00240             ret += ")";
00241         }
00242         break;
00243     case 4: //  a,b
00244         ret += numberToString(s_alpha);
00245         ret += ", ";
00246         ret += numberToString(s_beta);
00247         break;
00248     case 5: //  BEST ACTION,VALUE
00249         if( s_boxAction )
00250             ret = QString("[%1], ").arg(s_bestAction);
00251         else
00252             ret = s_bestAction + ", ";
00253         if( s_boxValue )
00254             ret += QString("[%1]").arg(s_bestValue);
00255         else
00256             ret += QString::number(s_bestValue);
00257         break;   
00258     default:
00259         break;
00260     }
00261     
00262     return ret;
00263 }
